      "content": "Sharp pain in your lower right abdomen can be alarming, but it's best to avoid self-medicating without understanding the cause. Ibuprofen and codeine can mask symptoms and potentially delay necessary treatment. It's important to consult a healthcare professional to get an accurate diagnosis and appropriate treatment. Try to rest and monitor if the pain persists or worsens, and seek medical attention if necessary.",
